Subject: [PATCH RFC 00/22] KVM: x86: hyper-v: Fine-grained access check to
 Hyper-V hypercalls and MSRs
Date: Tue, 13 Apr 2021 14:26:08 +0200
Message-Id: <20210413122630.975617-1-vkuznets@redhat.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
